title: Gerard Pique waves to fans at Camp Nou as he leaves the pitch for the final time | ESPN FC

media:group.media:title: Gerard Pique waves to fans at Camp Nou as he leaves the pitch for the final time | ESPN FC
media:group.media:description:
Gerard Pique receives hugs from his Barcelona teammates and a lengthy applause from fans at Camp Nou as he leaves the match in the second half against Almeria.
